%% Historic interval file flow - EtlScheduler path
%% Cluster DW ETL completion to IntervalAggregator reads DynamoDB
%% writes S3 files (verint, verintadherence, iexsftp, cxonewfm)
%% S3 events trigger VerintPublisher (REST) and IntervalPublisher (SFTP)
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant DW as Cluster DW<br/>SQL Server
    participant ES as EtlScheduler<br/>IHostedService
    participant AUR as Aurora MySQL
    participant IA as IntervalAggregator<br/>REST API
    participant DDB as DynamoDB
    participant S3 as S3 interval bucket<br/>IntegrationsWFMIntervalBucket
    participant QV as SqsVerintPublishQueue
    participant QI as SqsPublishQueue
    participant VP as VerintPublisher<br/>Java
    participant IP as IntervalPublisher
    participant V as Verint API<br/>per-tenant
    participant IXS as IEX SFTP<br/>per-tenant

    Note over ES: Timer fires every 60s
    ES->>AUR: CALL Interval_GetClusters
    AUR-->>ES: List of ClusterInfo

    loop For each cluster Task.Run
        ES->>ES: intervalEnd equals now.This15MinIncrement
        ES->>AUR: Interval_GetLastEtlRequest cluster COMPOSITE_ETL
        AUR-->>ES: lastSuccessful

        alt Not yet processed
            ES->>ES: wait PollDelayMinutes
            loop Every PollingPeriodSeconds
                ES->>DW: IC_GetETLData DW_SUMMARIZE_AGENT_LOG
                ES->>DW: IC_GetETLData DW_SUMMARIZE_CONTACT_LOG
                alt Both greater than intervalEnd
                    ES->>IA: POST /api/v1/Interval/cluster
                    ES->>AUR: Interval_UpdateLastEtlRequest
                    Note over ES: etl_interval_count plus plus
                end
            end
        end
    end

    Note over IA: Receives POST IntervalRequest
    IA->>DDB: DynamoConnector and DynamoReader
    DDB-->>IA: aggregated facts

    Note over IA: IntervalReportGenerator dispatch
    par 4 parallel report generators
        IA->>S3: PutObject verint slash BU TenantId slash yyMMdd.HHmm.json
        IA->>S3: PutObject verintadherence slash BU TenantId slash TTI_yyyyMMdd.HHmm.json
        IA->>S3: PutObject iexsftp slash Stack slash Tenant slash MMddyy.HHmm.xml
        IA->>S3: PutObject cxonewfm slash BU TenantId slash yyMMdd.HHmm.json
    end

    Note over S3: S3 event notifications fire
    S3->>QV: ObjectCreated event for verint and verintadherence
    S3->>QI: ObjectCreated event for iexsftp

    par Verint REST publishing
        QV->>VP: SqsQueueService receives
        VP->>VP: MessageProcessingService.getFileDetailsFromMessage
        VP->>S3: AwsS3Service.fetchFile
        alt filename starts with TTI underscore
            VP->>VP: AgentPerformanceService format
        else queue file
            VP->>VP: CSIQueuePerformanceService format
        end
        VP->>AUR: CALL External_GetAllTenantData per tenant
        VP->>V: POST formatted payload
    and IEX SFTP publishing
        QI->>IP: SqsClient receives
        IP->>IP: parse key Stack Tenant filename
        IP->>S3: GetObject XML
        IP->>AUR: CALL Interval_GetSftpConnectionsByTenantStack
        IP->>IXS: SFTP upload via Renci.SshNet
    end

    Note right of S3: cxonewfm picked up by external CxOne process. No in-repo consumer.
